system.benefits: God daemons will have +X added to their stats. 8 max ability and tactics slots.
system.description: A powerful individual. The God is just that, a god manifest in the form of a daemon. They usually are created when mortals try to reify a concept into a more conceivable form. The God has no need to set out on a Journey by nature of their being. More often than not, placating or even fighting the God is end of a Journey. The God is an entity of immaculate power and requires great power to wield.
